room_title: Escape room "The Incredible Machine" by ClockWise Escape Room in San Francisco
room_description: You have awakened to find yourselves in an odd place, another world, a Steam Punk dimension! You rub your eyes and see you’re in a workshop of sorts, with gears and gismos galore. What brought you here? How do you get back home? You have an hour to search the premises and figure out how to travel back to your world. Hurry or you’ll be stuck here forever!
